description: Describes the default KMS key for EBS encryption by default for your account in this Region. You can change the default KMS key for encryption by default using  ModifyEbsDefaultKmsKeyId or  ResetEbsDefaultKmsKeyId. For more information, see Amazon EBS encryption in the Amazon EBS User Guide.

nested_items.name: KmsKeyId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the default KMS key for encryption by default.
